pi-stomp (3.2.0-3) trixie; urgency=medium

  * Encoder: initialise decoder state before wiring GPIO callbacks. On a
    recovery->pi-stomp handoff, recovery releasing its pull-up on a shared
    encoder pin (nav 17/4, tweak1 12/25) glitches the line just as pi-stomp
    constructs its Encoder; gpiozero's initial event could fire the callback
    before prevNextCode existed, raising AttributeError in the lgpio callback
    thread and killing every rotary encoder (switches, being ADC-polled,
    still worked).

