    selector), GX Cabinet.
  * More EQ plugin types (parametric, graphic, custom).
  * Window decorations use analytic curves for consistent visuals.
  * Analytic rounded edges for dialogs.
  * Plugin windows match the visual style of regular windows.
  * Plugin window UI consistent with menus; vertical centering for large dialogs.
  * Analog controls aligned to pedal columns.
